    "Body": " As our Security Application Developer, you will be tasked to develop cryptography related security platforms, conduct security code reviews and testing services. In addition, you will be responsible for identifying application security risks and requirements for new projects and system developments. Requirements Develop cryptography related security platforms Perform manual code review and testing services Review logic flow and layout security requirements of the system Support the InfoSec team in the promotion of information security best practices and embedding information security within the development streams Skills and experiences required Solid development experience in the following computer languages: Rust / C++ Good understanding of cryptographic primitives, including RSA and ECC Experience in the following will be an advantage but not required: cross-platform mobile application development (iOS and Android) Knowing of Intel/ SGX, cryptography, multi-sign protocol and/or modern Blockchain systems will be an advantage You are also expected to: Demonstrate strong commitment to personal learning and development Detail minded with an analytical mindset Good communication skills with an ability to explain complex technical issues to non-technical business users Proficiency in both spoken and written English Benefits We offer an attractive compensation package working in a cutting-edge field of Fintech. Huge responsibilities from Day 1. Be the owner of your own learning curve. The possibilities are limitless and depend on you You get to work in a very dynamic environment and be part of an international team You will get to have involvement in developing a brand new product from scratch alongside with a talented team Skills Rust, C++, ECC, RSA Compensation SGD 5000 - SGD 8000 / month ", 
